    {
      "id": "PopularPost353067",
      "post_content": "Wow, the \\*\\*idea\\*\\* behind this is good, love the cost to cast it, just ![1](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=1&type=symbol), but then having to pay ![5](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=5&type=symbol) to ![Tap](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=tap&type=symbol) and use its ability? No thanks.  \n  \nThe problem is that the ability, for what it is, is overcosted. The cost to put the artifact into play is great, the sacrificing is ok (maybe I'd be fine with paying ![4](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=4&type=symbol) if it didn't require sacrificing the artifact), even dealing 3 to a creature - no choice between creature or player is not the end of the world, it's that cost of ![5](/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&name=5&type=symbol) to use the ability that drives me nuts.  \n  ",
      "posted_by": "Travelsonic",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost353067\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">Wow, the **idea** behind this is good, love the cost to cast it, just <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"1\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=1&amp;type=symbol\"/>, but then having to pay <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"5\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=5&amp;type=symbol\"/> to <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"Tap\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=tap&amp;type=symbol\"/> and use its ability?  No thanks.<br/><br/>The problem is that the ability, for what it is, is overcosted.  The cost to put the artifact into play is great, the sacrificing is ok (maybe I'd be fine with paying <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"4\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=4&amp;type=symbol\"/> if it didn't require sacrificing the artifact), even dealing 3 to a creature - no choice between creature or player is not the end of the world, it's that cost of <img align=\"absbottom\" alt=\"5\" src=\"/Handlers/Image.ashx?size=small&amp;name=5&amp;type=symbol\"/> to use the ability that drives me nuts.<br/><br/></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '353067'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy80792\">Travelsonic</span>\r\n  